            "liquid": "{%- comment -%} JACQ Trustpilot pill – klikbaar (nieuwe tab) {%- endcomment -%}\n\n<style>\n  .jacq-rating-pill{\n    display:inline-flex;\n    align-items:center;\n    gap:6px !important;\n    padding:4px 8px !important;                 /* ~2x */\n    border-radius:999px;\n\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14) !important;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.55) !important;\n\n    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n\n    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;\n    color:#ffffff !important;\n    max-width: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .jacq-rating-stars{\n    display:inline-flex;\n    gap:2px !important;                         /* ~2x */\n    line-height:0;\n    flex:0 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .jacq-star-box{\n    width:12px !important;                      /* ~2x */\n    height:12px !important;\n    border-radius:3px !important;\n    background:#00B67A;\n    display:inline-flex;\n    align-items:center;\n    justify-content:center;\n  }\n\n  .jacq-star-box--p20{\n    background: linear-gradient(to right, #00B67A 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.25) 20%);\n  }\n\n  .jacq-star{\n    width:10px !important;                      /* ~2x */\n    height:10px !important;\n    display:block;\n  }\n\n  .jacq-rating-text{\n    font-size:12px !important;                  /* ~2x */\n    line-height:1.15 !important;\n    font-weight:500;\n    opacity:.95;\n    color:#ffffff !important;\n    white-space: normal;\n    overflow-wrap:anywhere;\n  }\n\n  .jacq-trustpilot{ font-style: italic; }\n\n  @media (min-width: 990px){\n    .jacq-rating-text{\n      font-size:13px !important;                /* desktop iets groter */\n      white-space: nowrap;\n      overflow-wrap: normal;\n    }\n    .jacq-rating-text .jacq-mobile{ display:none !important; }\n    .jacq-rating-text .jacq-desktop{ display:inline !important; }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 989px){\n    .jacq-rating-text .jacq-desktop{ display:none !important; }\n    .jacq-rating-text .jacq-mobile{ display:inline !important; }\n  }\n\n  /* ✅ alleen link reset + klikbaar, verder exact hetzelfde */\n  a.jacq-rating-pill{\n    text-decoration:none;\n    color:inherit;\n    cursor:pointer;\n    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\n  }\n  a.jacq-rating-pill:focus-visible{\n    outline:none;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<a\n  class=\"jacq-rating-pill\"\n  href=\"https://nl.trustpilot.com/review/jacqeyewear.nl\"\n  target=\"_blank\"\n  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n  role=\"img\"\n  aria-label=\"Beoordeeld met een 4.3/5 op Trustpilot. lees wat onze klanten zeggen.\"\n>\n  <span class=\"jacq-rating-stars\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    {% for i in (1..4) %}\n      <span class=\"jacq-star-box\">\n        <svg class=\"jacq-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <path fill=\"#fff\" d=\"M12 17.3 6.2 20.7l1.6-6.7L2.6 9.7l6.9-.6L12 2.8l2.5 6.3 6.9.6-5.2 4.3 1.6 6.7z\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </span>\n    {% endfor %}\n\n    <span class=\"jacq-star-box jacq-star-box--p20\">\n      <svg class=\"jacq-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <path fill=\"#fff\" d=\"M12 17.3 6.2 20.7l1.6-6.7L2.6 9.7l6.9-.6L12 2.8l2.5 6.3 6.9.6-5.2 4.3 1.6 6.7z\"/>\n      </svg>\n    </span>\n  </span>\n\n  <span class=\"jacq-rating-text\">\n    <span class=\"jacq-mobile\">Beoordeeld met een 4.3/5 op Trustpilot </span>\n    <span class=\"jacq-desktop\">Beoordeeld met een 4.3/5 op <span class=\"jacq-trustpilot\">Trustpilot</span> · lees wat onze klanten zeggen</span>\n  </span>\n</a>"
          }
        },
