        "eyebrow": "",
        "heading": "Designed in London, for real homes",
        "text": "<p>Meave London started with something its founder, Meave Sinclair, couldn't stop thinking about. As an interior stylist in London, she spent her days making rooms feel calm and finished, only to see them let down by harsh, badly placed lighting.</p><p>So she designed a different kind of light. It has the warmth and proportions of a designer wall sconce, but it's completely wireless, so there's no drilling and no rewiring.</p>",
        "signature": "Meave Sinclair",
        "signature_role": "Founder, Meave London"
      }
